      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dents, fading paint, and some areas of surface rust. Mechanically, the car is currently running but exhibits a rough idle and will likely need major engine or transmission work in the near future. The interior is heavily worn with tears in the upholstery and non-functioning electronics. This is a project car sold as-is, ideal for someone looking for a parts vehicle or a complete restoration project.",
