    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention project lovers and restoration enthusiasts! This vehicle is ready for someone with a vision to take it on. While it currently needs some serious mechanical work and TLC to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic foundation for a dedicated hobbyist or anyone looking for a rewarding hands-on project. Grab this opportunity to breathe new life into a classic potential-filled ride!",
      "price": 3500.0,
